{
  "stem": "3022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But otherwise, internal administration was in the hands of the Jewish, Jewish [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "One time though, the Germans decided-- the gestapo sheriff came down, his henchman was Hoffman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they decided that besides inflicting physical damage, they are going to try to break our spirits.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they came to the leadership of the camp and they requested 20 people for execution the next morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they told them, unless you give us 20 people tomorrow, we'll come and we'll, we'll take you as first ones.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we'll take every 10th person in the camp, and we are going to shoot them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there was-- they suffered some-- something terrible happened to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were not aware of what was, what was the reason for it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Well, a meeting-- I, I know the story well, because I was witness to what was happening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "A meeting was called for the eldest in the camp to decide whom you were going to turn in, whom you're going to give them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Out of 2,000 some people, he had to give them 20 people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the people that were asked to come were, were people who in their life, at their hometowns, were prominent people, respected people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had some professors in the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We had people from the [NON-ENGLISH], intellectuals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the discussion took place, and various people were proposed for execution.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Somebody suggested, let's take the sick ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They have no chance of survival.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Others suggested, let's take the troublemakers, the ones who always cause a problem.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Let's take ones who are thieves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Let's-- different, different people were given, offered for different reason.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "However, some people felt that this was too difficult a decision to be made, and some more people were asked to come into the deliberation.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
